detail: Have you ever been cyberbullied, where someone was trying on purpose to harm you or be mean to you online, in texts, or group texts, or on social media (like Instagram or Snapchat)?
Has this happened to you in the past 12 months?
How often in the past 12 months?
valueInfo: 1, 1 time | 2, 2 times | 3, 3 times | 4, 4-9 times | 5, 10-19 times | 6, 20-39 times | 7, 40-49 times | 8, 50+ times

detail: Did they have more power, strength, or social influence than you? This could be because they were bigger, had more friends, were more popular, or had more power than you in another way?
Have you ever cyberbullied someone, where you purposefully tried to harm another person or be mean to them online, in texts or group texts, or on social media (like Instagram or Snapchat)?
Have you done this in the past 12 months?
How often in the past 12 months?
valueInfo: 1, 1 time | 2, 2 times | 3, 3 times | 4, 4-9 times | 5, 10-19 times | 6, 20-39 times | 7, 40-49 times | 8, 50+ times

detail: Did you have more power, strength, or social influence than the person you were cyberbullying? This could be because you were bigger than this person, had more friends, were more popular, or had more power than that person in another way?
